text: Pema Tshering is an archer from Bhutan. Tshering competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics.Pema TSHERING He was born on 15 July 1951.Pema Tshering == References == Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Bhutanese archers Category:Olympians for Bhutan
